\fs28 \cf0 A LARP-Capitalist Simulator \'97 Design Document\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\fs24 \cf0 Premise:
\f1\b0  You are not building a real business. You are building the 
\f2\i appearance
\f1\i0  of one, one post at a time, until the appearance starts generating real money. Every mechanic in this doc maps directly onto AdVenture Capitalist's systems (documented in the previous breakdown), reskinned around fabricated online authority instead of physical businesses.\
Tone: satirical, self-aware. The game knows the player is faking it. Copy should wink at hustle-culture ("7 Habits of Highly Deceptive People," "Manifested $10K This Morning 
\f3 \uc0\u55357 \u56911 
\f1 ").\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
