\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 \strokec2 9. Trends (the "events")\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 Time-limited (2\'964 day) live events tied to a fake news cycle ("AI Panic Week," "Recession Core Aesthetic") that unlock a bonus Hustle set, a unique Ghostwriter, and exclusive cosmetic rewards. Matches AdCap's event structure directly, including scarcity \'97 miss the window, miss the exclusive reward.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa298\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 10. Network (the "Capitalist Connections" collectible layer)\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 Collectible cards representing fellow fake-guru NPCs ("The Crypto Whisperer," "The 4am Cold Plunge Guy"). Earning 1 of a card = bronze, 3 = gold, 10 = platinum, each tier granting a small passive bonus; completing a full platform's set grants a large flat speed or profit boost, mirroring AdCap's blue/gold/platinum manager-card system. Cards drop from Trends or are purchased with Ad Spend.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa298\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 11. Personas (the "suits/badges")\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 Equippable cosmetic identities \'97 "Girlboss," "Dropout Founder," "Ex-Hedge-Fund Whistleblower" \'97 that apply flat profit multipliers to specific platforms, same function as AdCap's outfit system. Only a limited number equippable at once, forcing a build choice.\
